{
  "chapter": 182,
  "chapter_summary": "第182章\"奸人授首\"讲述项少龙与李园联手击败春申君、李令叛乱集团的决战。春申君府和夜郎王府先后被攻破，李令被擒。项少龙劝李园将打击范围局限于首恶，李园从之。李嫣嫣亲审李权、李令，揭露五年前二人侵犯她的往事，亲手以淬毒匕首刺杀李权，项少龙阻止李令侮辱李嫣嫣。李嫣嫣要求项少龙杀李令，项少龙拒绝杀无力反抗之人，交由李园和庄夫人处置。次日早朝，春申君、斗介、成素宁三人被斩首，李园升任右丞相，庄保义被确认为滇国储君。善柔透露追踪田单的经历，滕翼查到田单去向。然而黄昏时传来噩耗：徐先出事，田单暗中由陆路潜返齐国，吕不韦的阴谋破坏了咸阳的势力平衡。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_li_ling",
      "text": "李令老兄！别来无恙啊！",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "把他绑起来，押到车上，我们回滇王府去。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "这些夜郎人和李令的滇兵窝囊得很，府内又无特别防御部署，给我们以强弩、火箭逐屋冲杀，连阻挡半刻都办不到，只轻伤我们十多人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 46,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "今晚的事，我李园会铭记于心，无论将来秦、楚发生什么事，我仍是两位的朋友。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "我和李兄沙场见面的机会微乎其微，且我还有尽早退隐之意，李兄不用担心。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "speaker_name": "楼无心",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "找不到田单，据说他今早已离开寿春，这事须问春申君才行。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "旦楚等仍未抵此处，他理该尚未返齐，唉！不过也很难说。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 70,
      "line_end": 72
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "speaker_name": "楼无心",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "内城已在控制之下，可开始搜捕奸党的行动了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 74,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李兄可否把打击的对象局限在春申君等几个人身上？报仇雪恨始终不是最佳的解决办法。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "text": "若连这样的事都办不到，怎报得项兄的恩典，一切照项兄的意思办吧！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_lou_wu_xin",
      "text": "你负责为我通知内城所有大臣将领，今趟之事，只是春申君、李权和成素宁三人意图谋反，与其他人全无牵连，除这三人的直系男子亲属外，妇女均可以安返娘家，婢仆则另行处置。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 83
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "算你这人有点良心，终肯来对付田单。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_shan_rou",
      "text": "你怎会混到春申君府去的呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "柔姊一直追踪田单，猜到他由咸阳回齐时必会道经寿春，又知他与春申君有勾结，于是卖身为婢，到春申君府伺候。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 113
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "现在田单到了哪里去呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他是去与旦楚会合，据说他正循淮河坐船东下，人家正苦恼不知如何措置，幸好你来了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_teng_yi",
      "speaker_name": "滕翼",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "查到田单的去向了，他今早秘密出城，坐船到城阳去与旦楚的伤兵残军会合，没有十天半月，都回不到齐国，我们还有足够时间准备。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 123
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wu_guang",
      "speaker_name": "乌光",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "太后在外堂等候项爷！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_quan",
      "speaker_name": "李权",
      "listener": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "text": "太后请为老臣作主……",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": "char_li_quan",
      "text": "闭嘴！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "除万将军外，其他人请出去。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": "char_li_quan",
      "text": "你们两人还记得五年前发生的事吗？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_quan",
      "speaker_name": "李权",
      "listener": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "text": "嫣嫣！别忘记我是你的堂叔，一向都疼爱你……",
      "tone": "颤声",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": "char_li_quan",
      "text": "正因为一个是我的堂叔，一个是我的堂兄，我才终身忘不了你们禽兽不如的行为。若是外人，我或者还能忍受下去。我作践自己的身体，为的就是今天。李权你给我滚过来。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 158,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_quan",
      "speaker_name": "李权",
      "listener": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "text": "太后饶命！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_ling",
      "speaker_name": "李令",
      "listener": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "text": "什么太后，还不是给我李令骑……",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你给我杀了李令好吗？",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "text": "我不惯杀没有还手之力的人，让我找别人代劳如何？",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 185
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "你是个真正的好人，好吧！",
      "tone": "欣慰",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 188,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "太后心情不好，让她静静吧！李权完蛋了，李令就交给你们。",
      "tone": "低声",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yan_yan",
      "speaker_name": "李嫣嫣",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不！我要亲眼看着他被处决！",
      "tone": "坚决",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不要问我别后的情况，想知道就问她们两个吧！本姑娘绝不会重复的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "真的很挂念你，每个月至少想一次。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "外面情况如何？",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 224
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "text": "现在只等斗介明天上朝，李园派了个斗介信任的人去告诉他，讹称我和李园均给春申君杀了，好诓得他没有戒备下进城。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 227
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ji_yan_ran",
      "speaker_name": "纪嫣然",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "斗介孤掌难鸣，还有什么作为？王城岂是这么容易攻破，下面的人亦不肯陪他把身家性命孤注一掷，谁的家族亲人不是居于城内。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 230,
      "line_end": 231
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_zhi",
      "speaker_name": "赵致",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "夜了！夫君不如沐浴休息，今晚让柔姊陪你。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 236,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他算什么东西，谁会陪他？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "斗介中计了，刚进城便给武瞻拿着，现在武瞻执掌军符，出城接收他的军队。",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "徐先是否出事了？",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 278
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "不但徐先出事，田单原来连春申君都骗了，暗里由陆路潜返齐国。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 281
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_long_yang_jun",
      "speaker_name": "龙阳君",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "他是怕给卷入这次暗杀中，所以先行溜走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shan_rou",
      "speaker_name": "善柔",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "快追！我知道如何可以把他截着。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 182,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    }
  ],
